{"root":{"data":{"id":"c5r798n8ke80","created":1600503829003,"text":"论题和结论是什么","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"c6zla9jhmjs0","created":1605012042950,"text":"0，第一步就得培养找准论题和结论的能力；学完这章，我们应该能回答第一个关键“论题和结论是什么”"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"c5r9wmicl940","created":1600511303778,"text":"1，“是什么”问题和“应不应该”问题","expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"c5ra01d7ots0","created":1600511571212,"text":"描述性论题：有关世界过去、现在、未来是什么样的问题","expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"c6zlejybcu00","created":1605012379071,"text":"例1，音乐学习是不是有助于提供一个人得数学能力？"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"c6zlf27cy000","created":1605012418800,"text":"例2，家庭暴力最常见得诱因是什么？"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"c6zlfa03uzs0","created":1605012435775,"text":"例3，服用帕罗西丁是不是治疗抑郁症得有效手段？"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"c6zlfo0y55s0","created":1605012466301,"text":"例4，美国2016年医疗保险得花费将会达到多少？"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"c6zlgbstbfk0","created":1605012518052,"text":"例5，伊利诺伊大学心理学研究所的水平怎么样？"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"c5ra0okuc1s0","created":1600511621739,"text":"规定性论题：有关世界应该是什么样的问题","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"c6zlj1fbj7k0","created":1605012730561,"text":"例1，公立学校应不应该教授智能设计？"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"c6zljhgoek80","created":1605012765471,"text":"例2，对医疗补助欺诈应该采取什么措施？"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"c6zljug6mwg0","created":1605012793740,"text":"例3，我们应该立法禁止使用。。。"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"c5ra2dbb6q00","created":1600511753947,"text":"2，他到底在说什么啊","expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"c5ra2orknsw0","created":1600511778875,"text":"对方直接告诉你问题或论题","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"c5ra3086v740","created":1600511803824,"text":"当没有明确问题或论题时，可以先去找结论","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"c5ra3wuylqg0","created":1600511874858,"text":"论题需要符合“论题”的界定标准","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"c5ra47wonvs0","created":1600511898907,"text":"结论是什么？它是作者或演说者希望你接受的信息","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"c5ra4utxg5k0","created":1600511948806,"text":"3，他想让我相信什么结论","expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"c5s3vh5o7j40","created":1600595847061,"text":"首先要问，希望证明的是什么，或者和我交流的这个人主要观点是什么？","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"c5s3wu1vxd40","created":1600595953494,"text":"推理的基本结构：甲之所以成立是因为乙。甲是结论，乙是结论的支撑材料。","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"c5s3xjjpea00","created":1600596008991,"text":"没有提供相应陈述来支撑的断言，不能称为结论，这个叫纯观点。","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"c5s3ybqgrmg0","created":1600596070350,"text":"你相信一个陈述是因为你认为它有其他看法所支撑，这就是在进行推理。","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"c6zltjvvys80","created":1605013554386,"text":"接下来我们所关心的是：基于支撑这一论断的所有材料，我应不应该接受这个结论？"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"c5ra4zn6nf40","created":1600511959282,"text":"4，找到结论有线索可循","expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"c5s3z1gj9q80","created":1600596126346,"text":"线索1. 论题是什么？","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"c5s3z99rar40","created":1600596143350,"text":"线索2. 寻找指示词：因此，表明，由此可知，由此得出，因此可以断定，我要说的重点是，显示出，证明，告诉我们，问题的实质。。。","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"c5s409kyzxs0","created":1600596222393,"text":"线索3. 在可能的位置查看一下","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"c5s40ifb8qw0","created":1600596241641,"text":"线索4. 记住不可能作为结论的东西","expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"c5s41az7a4w0","created":1600596303794,"text":"例句","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"c5s41dab9bk0","created":1600596308819,"text":"数据","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"c5s41esrpps0","created":1600596312112,"text":"定义","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"c5s41hbue1c0","created":1600596317619,"text":"背景资料","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"c5s41jdttbc0","created":1600596322093,"text":"证据","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"c5s40oanvj40","created":1600596254421,"text":"线索5. 检查一下交流的语境和作者的背景","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"c5s40wwsku80","created":1600596273173,"text":"线索6. 问一问“所以呢？”","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"c5ra53x68680","created":1600511968593,"text":"5，轮到你自己写时，可得吸取教训","expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"c5s44vuuf2o0","created":1600596584335,"text":"无法建立起沟通的桥梁是批判性思维的最大障碍","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"c5s42xepy5c0","created":1600596430986,"text":"因为","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"c5s438gtuhs0","created":1600596455058,"text":"1. 读者无法听到我们内心的真实想法","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"c5s43oybgrc0","created":1600596490944,"text":"2. 无法看透我们许多隐藏的看法","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"c5s43x6z5cg0","created":1600596508883,"text":"3. 不知道我们的价值观和背景","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"c5s443bxyvk0","created":1600596522243,"text":"4. 对我们研究过程或构思腹稿一无所知","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"c5s4azobl2o0","created":1600597062833,"text":"所以我们要清楚表达自己的意思或观点，建立起沟通桥梁","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"c5s45qg06wg0","created":1600596650918,"text":"将论题范围尽量缩小","expandState":"expand","layout_left_offset":{"x":-72,"y":25}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"c5s46obpx3c0","created":1600596724670,"text":"花时间确定一下你的论题，有没有一个清楚明确的论题，是区分成不成熟的一个重要标志","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"c5s47haawmw0","created":1600596787711,"text":"不要过于贪心，一次说明一个论题，因为篇幅有限","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"c5s45xub3bk0","created":1600596667021,"text":"引导读者得出你的结论","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"c5s47y2uj3c0","created":1600596824265,"text":"老老实实把结论说出来，而且说的清楚明白，这是在帮助你的读者或者听众","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"c5s48e9n7og0","created":1600596859505,"text":"让你的结论一目了然，不仅节省了读者的精力，而且可以提高文章的逻辑度","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"c5s48zscqo00","created":1600596906349,"text":"必须竭尽所能地组织好自己的思想，然后明白无误地表达出来","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]}]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}